name: Beelzebub - Bronze Armor
description: Beelzebub known as the "Lord of the Flyers", or the "Lord of the Flies". Beelzebub is a name derived from a Philistine god, formerly worshiped in Ekron, and later adopted by some Abrahamic religions as a major demon. The name Beelzebub is associated with the Canaanite god Baal.
